{"tid":2150903,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"菅義偉︰會聯合其他國家應對香港問題","createTime":"2020-08-11T06:35:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T10:00:57.000Z","uid":21470,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fa9c75bff3244eb61a8657707a356c7c58d2f847","tid":2150903,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:35:11.000Z","msg":"菅義偉︰會向中方表達香港問題的立場 <br />\n2020-08-11 12:26 <br />\n<br />\n日本內閣官防長官菅義偉回應壹傳媒創辦人黎智英等10人被捕，指嚴重關切和密切注視香港情況。他指香港是日本的重要伙伴，兩地有緊密的經貿關係和人員交流，日方多次重申香港須維持自由開放的體系，並在一國兩制下民主和穩定發展，<span class=\"gold\">日方會透過不同機會，包括兩國外長通電話時向中方表達有關立場，亦會聯合其他國家合適應對。</span><br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2351640\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2351640&d=ukYMMJnQLP7OtwhP8v88lD2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=c4149b87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2351640</a>"},{"pid":"3545d6ce004f2a8c9e1c8acaa208fa2c21ed5c50","tid":2150903,"uid":3149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:43:55.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"920ae30d09773df9b7e0d390fabfa11a8d6c38b8","tid":2150903,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:44:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a82b47251865a3cb05054e44c84ed7e13c1dc859","tid":2150903,"uid":243677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:44:37.000Z","msg":"日本 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a558af6aaeab2ab084a0b2a6c37704324fde2661","tid":2150903,"uid":64953,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:45:14.000Z","msg":"制裁三萬警我已經接受"},{